{"tid":774160,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國遊客旅遊開支大增4成 日本為最愛國家","createTime":"2018-08-10T06:10:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-10T15:07:37.000Z","uid":20058,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f18f4bb02c1cc8c0f4ed26f89878befc77c53a90","tid":774160,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T06:10:37.000Z","msg":"中國人好鍾意去旅行，相信大家都知啦，去到世界各地任何地方都幾乎見到中國旅客；<a href=\"http://酒店預訂網站Hotels.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97%E9%A0%90%E8%A8%82%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99Hotels.com&d=oHw83IesGPoPlBdW0TbFUL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=3299900d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">酒店預訂網站Hotels.com</a>日前就公佈咗最近統計數字，2017年中國旅客嘅旅遊開支大增4成！其中中國嘅90後、00後隨住年齡已經開始周圍飛，成為中國旅客其中一個重大開支嘅支柱。報告話6成00後中國旅客揀選地點旅行好大程度係因為明星效應，而且去旅行最重要係要放上社交網體建立形象。至於旅行活動，7成人表示係希望食到當地特色美食、43%人就想買當地名產、38%人想買奢侈品。至於熱門目的地方面，日本仍然係第一位，有39%，香港就跌落第二位嘅37%，第三則為美國有30%。其次就要數「未來12個月內有意初次遊覽」十大目的地。第一位則為澳洲，有19%；第二位加拿大，有18%；第三為法國，有14%。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/travel/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%81%8A%E5%AE%A2%E6%97%85%E9%81%8A%E9%96%8B%E6%94%AF%E5%A4%A7%E5%A2%9E4%E6%88%90-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E7%82%BA%E6%9C%80%E6%84%9B%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6-2004813020692534.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Ftravel%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%2581%258A%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E6%2597%2585%25E9%2581%258A%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%2594%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25A2%259E4%25E6%2588%2590-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E7%2582%25BA%25E6%259C%2580%25E6%2584%259B%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%25B6-2004813020692534.html&d=oHw83IesGPoPlBdW0TbFUL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=8b9a6bb6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/travel/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%81%8A%E5%AE%A2%E6%97%85%E9%81%8A%E9%96%8B%E6%94%AF%E5%A4%A7%E5%A2%9E4%E6%88%90-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E7%82%BA%E6%9C%80%E6%84%9B%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6-2004813020692534.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img s